Package org.svvrl.goal.core.aut.sdbw

Class SDBW

java.lang.Object
org.svvrl.goal.core.aut.sdbw.SDBW
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.EventListener, AutomatonListener
public class SDBW
extends java.lang.Object
implements AutomatonListener
This class provides a wrapper of an automaton as a semi-deterministic Büchi automaton (SDBW). By definition, the states of an SDBW are partitioned into two disjoint sets N and D where D is deterministic and all accepting states are contained in D.
Author:
Ming-Hsien Tsai
